
Run shell command with arguments in 'create' action on 'rkt' mode. For example:

eveadm rkt create --image url
eveadm rkt create image_uuid

Usage:
  eveadm rkt create url/uuid [flags]

Flags:
  -h, --help                      help for create
  -i, --image                     Work with images
      --no-overlay                Run without overlay
      --paused                    Run paused (default true)
      --stage1-path string        Stage1 path (default "/usr/sbin/stage1-xen.aci")
      --uuid-file-save string     File to save uuid
      --xen-cfg-filename string   File with xen cfg for stage1

Global Flags:
      --config string             config file (default is $HOME/.eveadm.yaml)
      --dir string                RKT data dir
      --insecure-options string   RKT insecure-options (default "image")
      --stage1-type string        Type of stage1 (xen or general) (default "xen")
  -t, --timeout string            Actions timeout in minutes
  -v, --verbose                   Verbose execution
